OL,3,CMan, 48, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after woman found dead
OL,6,FA 48-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after a woman was
OL,8,Ffound dead at a property in Bracknell.
OL,10,FPolice were called to an address in
OL,11,FBirkdale on Wednesday morning,
OL,12,Ffollowing reports that a 40-year-old
OL,13,Fwoman had sustained a head injury.
OL,15,FShe was later pronounced dead at the
OL,16,Fscene.
OL,18,FHer next of kin have been informed and
OL,19,Fa formal identification will take
OL,20,Fplace in due course.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
