OL,3,CMan, 48, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after woman found dead
OL,6,FThe man arrested remains in police
OL,7,Fcustody and officers will continue a
OL,8,Fpresence at the scene while
OL,9,Finvestigations continue.
OL,11,FThames Valley Police Senior
OL,12,Finvestigating officer Detective Chief
OL,13,FInspector Stuart Brangwin said: "Our
OL,14,Fthoughts are with the family and loved
OL,15,Fones of the woman at this incredibly
OL,16,Fdifficult time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
