PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784204303
OL,3,CMan, 48, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after woman found dead
OL,6,F"We are in the early stages of a
OL,7,Fcomplex investigation and are pursuing
OL,8,Fa number of lines of enquiry to
OL,9,Festablish the full circumstances
OL,10,Fsurrounding her death."
OL,12,FHe said that the Force does not
OL,13,Fbelieve there is "any wider risk to
OL,14,Fthe public".
OL,16,FIt's asking people to avoid online
OL,17,Fspeculation which may cause
OL,18,F"additional distress to those
OL,19,Faffected".
